Say '''Buldon''' et kumapat ya klase baley ed luyag na [[Maguindanao]], [[Pilipinas]]. Unong ed 2010 Census, say papulasyon to et 33,729 totoo. Walay kabaleg tan sukat to ya 429.4 sq. km. Sikato et walad unaan ya distrito. Say zip code to et 9615.	
	
